lead_paragraph: Michael Pineda is finally putting it together for the New York Yankees. Carlos Beltran and Starlin Castro, meanwhile, have provided consistent power all season.

headline.print_headline: Beltran, Castro Power Pineda and Yankees Past Angels 6-3
